  "2026-02-19T21:34:16.277Z",cursor-maintainer,"Planned change-set: add deterministic integration coverage for CLI exit-code mapping paths (usage, not-found, conflict, dependency-failed, generic failure), validate existing error model contracts in src/core/shared/errors.ts and src/cli/main.ts, then run pm test + test-all regression sweeps with 100% coverage evidence."
  "2026-02-19T21:58:54.806Z",cursor-maintainer,"Implemented exit-code hardening for generic-failure path by adding integration coverage in tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts (new test: returns generic-failure exit code for unexpected init filesystem errors), which validates top-level unknown-error mapping to exit code 1 while preserving existing checks for usage/not-found/conflict/dependency-failed. Evidence: pm test pm-siz --run --timeout 2400 --json passed all linked tests (3/3); pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 2400 --json passed totals items=8 linked_tests=36 passed=35 failed=0 skipped=1; pm test-all --status closed --timeout 2400 --json passed totals items=16 linked_tests=44 passed=41 failed=0 skipped=3; coverage remains 100% statements/branches/functions/lines."
